// "Flamewrath deals 50% reduced damage, but does not consume the blaze stack" (Mechanics, common,
// unique). Installs the "flamewrath_no_consume" flag: a real Pre hook (ability/hooks.rs's
// FlamewrathNoConsume, halving "damage") PLUS a direct ActiveHooks read at the blaze-removal
// special-case in execute.rs that skips the RemoveStatusEvent.
(
    id: "flamewrath_no_consume_common",
    display_name: "Lingering Wrath",
    ability_scope: Some("flamewrath"),
    rarity: Common,
    uniqueness: Exclusive,
    effect: Behavior("flamewrath_no_consume"),
)
